headline: Keysight Expands USB Standards Support in System Designer for USB
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., May 07, 2025--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS) announced today the launch of System Designer for USB, its latest solution for high-speed digital USB (Universal Serial Bus) design tailored to personal computers, mobile devices, and edge AI applications.
